traits.name: Volcanic
traits.description: A volatile world marked by intense volcanic activity, creating a hazardous environment with the potential for valuable resource extraction, such as rare metals and geothermal energy.

traits.name: Sprawling Cities
traits.description: Expansive urban centers that stretch across the landscape, boasting advanced infrastructure and diverse populations.

traits.name: Dry Seabeds
traits.description: Vast, desolate landscapes that once held oceans, now exposing the remnants of ancient marine life and providing opportunities for the discovery of valuable resources.

traits.name: Fossils
traits.description: A waypoint rich in the remains of ancient life, offering a valuable window into the past and the potential for scientific discovery.

traits.name: Marketplace
traits.description: A thriving center of commerce where traders from across the galaxy gather to buy, sell, and exchange goods.
